article.description: — Collin Welp recorded 19 points and 12 rebounds to lift UC Irvine to a 75-64 win over UC San Diego on Saturday.
article.headline: Welp carries UC Irvine over UC San Diego 75-64
article.linkText: Welp carries UC Irvine over UC San Diego 75-64
article.story: IRVINE, Calif. -- — Collin Welp recorded 19 points and 12 rebounds to lift UC Irvine to a 75-64 win over UC San Diego on Saturday. Dawson Baker had 18 points for UC Irvine (14-8, 11-4 Big West Conference). Hugh Baxter scored a career-high 28 points for the Tritons (5-10, 2-10). Bryce Pope added 10 points. Mikey Howell had eight assists. The Anteaters remain undefeated in three games against the Tritons this season. Most recently, UC Irvine defeated UC San Diego 80-55 on Friday. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
